From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Patric Stout <github@truebrain.nl>
Date: Sun, 5 Jul 2026 09:44:50 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 06/17] fix: compile on case sensitive filesystems

For the include folder, more entries were using lower-case to
include from it than upper-case. It also makes most sense, as
the common naming of "include" folder is in lower case.
